  + [first_missing_feature] is no_theorem_converting_velocity_enstrophy_cutoff_budgets_to_same_cylinder_pressure_smallness
  + [Deep_Research_Priority_Gate] is conditionally_ready
    = trigger: only if a specific theorem family for velocity-enstrophy-to-pressure projection smallness is selected

& [DevelopedUnderstanding] is the current shape of meaning
  + [old_shape] is map source pressure-tail components to p_h, p_0, projected-pressure remainder, or outside status
  + [new_shape] is the mapping succeeds only negatively: p_h is absent, p_0/remainder inputs are not pressure outputs, and cutoff/scale terms remain outside pressure-smallness authority
  + [meaning_gained] is the pressure bridge cannot be advanced by relabeling the source tail; it would require a new theorem turning these budgets into pressure smallness
  + [proof_promotion_status] is blocked
  + [lock_mass_change] is none

& [NextBoundedMotion] is follow-up
